i got server (omfg pkz v2) and my client is csk. i dont know if it something to do with no-ip but i tried both no-ip and hamachi.

thank you,

.::goblin k.o::.

If you have linksys wireless or any other wireless modem/internet, you can NOT host a server, if that isn’t the problem there is probley something wrong in the “system” notepad
[/quote]
DUDE DO U EVEN KNOW WUT UR SAYING?!?!

DONT LISTEN TO HIM

THAT AINT TRUE[/quote]

Yes, infact I do know what I am saying. When I told my friend the IP address when I had my knew linksys wireless modem plugged in, and he went to log in he couldn’t, but I could. We thought it was just his computer, so we had another friend try, and he couldn’t either, so then I unplugged my linksys wireless modem and told them the IP and it worked. So please do not flame me for saying something that is TRUE, something that I know is true because I experienced it.
